Słońsko () is a village in the administrative district of &lt;a href="Gmina%20Inowroc%C5%82aw"&gt;Gmina Inowrocław&lt;/a&gt;, within &lt;a href="Inowroc%C5%82aw%20County"&gt;Inowrocław County&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="Kuyavian-Pomeranian%20Voivodeship"&gt;Kuyavian-Pomeranian Voivodeship&lt;/a&gt;, in north-central &lt;a href="Poland"&gt;Poland&lt;/a&gt;. It lies approximately north-east of &lt;a href="Inowroc%C5%82aw"&gt;Inowrocław&lt;/a&gt;, south-west of Toruń, and south-east of Bydgoszcz.
